::plast_in_adult::
In adult mammals, neurogenesis occurs mainly in:
{
~Neocortex
~Cerebellum
=Dentate gyrus #Adult neurogenesis is restricted to the dentate gyrus.
~Amygdala
}

::plast_approximately_how::
