{
~70
=700 #About 700 new neurons are generated daily.
~7,000
~70,000
}

::plast_pattern_separation::
Pattern separation refers to:
{
~Strengthening similar memories
=Separating similar experiences into distinct representations #Pattern separation reduces interference.
~Deleting overlapping memories
~Reducing memory precision
}

::plast_the_dentate::
The dentate gyrus is thought to support:
{
~Motor planning
~Emotion regulation
=Pattern separation #Dentate gyrus helps separate similar contexts.
~Visual perception
}

::plast_systems_consolidation::
