::epigenetics_overall_epigenetic::
Overall, epigenetic mechanisms link:
{
~Genes to mutations
=Experience to long-term brain function #They provide a biological bridge between experience and behavior.
~Stress to DNA damage
~Environment to genetics only during development
}

